{"tid":843724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美海軍神盾艦 再闖南海中共人造島礁12浬內","createTime":"2018-10-01T11:06:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-01T12:00:11.000Z","uid":79563,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"9785a2f7c59af28585fe9087808b4c0c16371c58","tid":843724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:06:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/bJtsVGmv/DDG-73.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FbJtsVGmv%2FDDG-73.jpg&h=ad62e6b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ydn.com.tw/News/307155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ydn.com.tw%2FNews%2F307155&d=wxCBMOCrh%2F4zoxv4IeR4H5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=37c32929\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ydn.com.tw/News/307155</a><br />\n<br />\n「美國之音」、「有線電視新聞網」（CNN）等外媒30日報導，美國海軍神盾驅逐艦 「狄卡特號」（DDG 73）駛入中共南海人工島礁12海里範圍內，強調維護自由航行權的決心。<br />\n<br />\n　五角大廈官員表示，「狄卡特號」在執行自由航行任務時，駛入南薰礁和赤瓜礁等中共人工島礁的12海里範圍內，強調「所有行動皆符合國際法」，並稱此行動的用意為「反制過度的主權聲索」。<br />\n<br />\n　美「中」近期除了在貿易上僵持不下外，南海問題也是雙方角力的重要領域；近期美軍不僅數次派艦駛過中共人工島礁，也讓B-52轟炸機於相關區域活動，希望嚇阻中共的野心。"},{"pid":"d29d8f61cede67642cbadb279b2ab6175be7b24d","tid":843724,"uid":163350,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:06:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d7cf4cfb2d1656156986350acf904d32c864f0a1","tid":843724,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:08:33.000Z","msg":"永遠唔見遼寧廢輪進入關島12浬內<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a52671fa0baf0f665104846eecd292b15fa08cb","tid":843724,"uid":98232,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-01T11:09:01.000Z","msg":"屌 人地填島果時都一直闖緊<br />\n有咩作為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img s